                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">Policeman. M.</hi> 58). I produce a certificate (<hi rend="italic">Read.</hi>—" <hi rend="italic">Central Criminal Court, Richard Pitts convicted of larceny, Nov.</hi> 1847, <hi rend="italic">transported seven years.".</hi>—I was present at the trial—Pitts is the person there mentioned.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>.—<hi rend="largeCaps">ALLEN</hi>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18611021-896-punishment-61" type="punishmentDescription">
